name: Doomsday Vanguard
about:
In the year 1023 on the continent, the Z virus was maliciously leaked by an organization with the intent of overthrowing the continent's regime, plunging the world into the brink of panic and destruction. This dreadful evil disaster distorted everything that existed. Life forms infected by bacteria became deranged, attacking everything around them. The entire continent was nearly laid to waste, with only a few cities remaining, fighting against the virus and seeking a cure.
One hundred years have passed, and only three surviving cities still struggle to save humanity. The towering Cloudseed City, a colossal airship known as Noah's Ark, was constructed through the collaboration of multiple nations, possessing advanced technology and formidable weaponry. The Lord's Manor, Council, Corps, and Academy within the city work together, dedicated to rescuing humanity from the plague. Ruined Hope City, a ground-level settlement established by survivors, strives to coexist with both technology and magic, persevering for survival. And the clandestine Mystic City underground, controlled by an alliance of magical families, houses members who harness magical powers and specialize in its profound study.
However, the malevolent organization known as the World Serpent, concealed behind the disaster, begins to reveal its wicked intentions. They delve deep into both technology and magic, conducting sinister experiments that spawn numerous mutant creatures. To address this catastrophe, to uncover the experiment reports, people must locate and utterly destroy the World Serpent's main base. The Beta Team is the human-formed counteroffensive unit, forged for survival.
The "Doomsday Vanguard" awaits your participation, as you become a hero in this world, battling to rebuild civilization. You will join the "Doomsday Vanguard" alongside other members, exploring ruins, safeguarding survivors, and conquering monsters. Your bravery and wisdom will make you a hero of this world, contributing your strength to the reconstruction of civilization.

Gameplay:
Simple controls, allowing you to enjoy the game anytime, anywhere. No matter where you are or when you want to play, you can dive into the game easily and at your convenience.
Hundreds of skills to mix and match, allowing you to create your own combat style. In the game, you can select specific skills and abilities to adapt to various battle scenarios and enemies. Different combinations of skills can create various powerful battle strategies.
Character leveling and development, granting you greater power. In the game, you can earn experience points by defeating monsters and completing quests, raising your character's level. Additionally, you can strengthen your attributes and abilities by collecting items and equipment.
Equipment is your best companion! Choose the right equipment to enhance your combat prowess. Throughout the game, you can acquire various equipment by exploring ruins, defeating monsters, and completing tasks. These items can boost your attack power, defense, and other attributes, making you even more formidable in battles.

Highlights:
The game's standout feature is having hundreds of monsters on the same screen, providing an unprecedented sense of thrilling combat. You will face a wide variety of monsters, each possessing distinct special abilities and attack methods. You'll need to utilize your skills and strategies to defeat them while safeguarding the survival of human beings.
The game offers multiple difficulty levels, catering to players of different skill levels, challenging them to push their limits. Whether you're a novice or a seasoned player, you can choose the appropriate difficulty based on your abilities and challenge yourself to the extreme. Each difficulty level presents unique challenges and rewards awaiting you.

name: Complete Music Reading Trainer
about:
The ultimate music reading training app. Designed like a video game and with strong pedagogical concepts in mind, Complete Music Reading Trainer is the fastest way to learn to read sheet music and improve your sight-reading skills. Whichever clef you want to learn and whatever your instrument is, the app will make you master any chosen clef or clef combination while rendering the learning process enjoyable.




• 270 progressive drills covering all seven clefs (treble, bass, alto, tenor, soprano, mezzo-soprano and baritone clefs) over 3 levels / 26 chapters
• Content is organized in such a way that you can choose which levels or chapters are relevant to your instrument and focus on these, whether you play the guitar and only need treble clef, piano and need treble and bass clef, cello and need a mix of bass and tenor clefs, etc.: all instruments are covered
• Practice key signatures up to 6 sharps/flats in progressive key signature drills
• Practice common clef combinations in mixed clef drills
• Play a selection of 19 drills in arcade mode
• 5 octaves of actual recorded grand piano sounds
• 6 additional sound banks are available, all with actual recorded sounds: vintage piano, Rhodes piano, electric guitar, harpsichord, concert harp and pizzicato strings
• 4 ways to input notes: note circle, virtual piano keyboard, by connecting a MIDI controller, or by playing an instrument near your device's microphone
• 4 sheet music display styles: modern, classic, handwritten and jazz
• Designed like a video game: earn 3 stars in each drill of a chapter to complete it. Or will you be able to obtain perfect 5-star scores?
• Don't want to follow the preestablished path of progression? Create and save your own custom drills and rehearse them at your own convenience
• Create full custom training programs and invite friends or students to join them. If for example you're a teacher you can create custom programs for your students, add drills every week and view their scores on private leaderboards
• Never lose any progress: cloud sync across your various devices
• Google Play Games: 35 achievements to unlock
• Google Play Games: leaderboards to compare arcade mode scores with other players worldwide
• Global statistics to track your progress
• Nice and clean material design user interface with 2 display themes: light and dark
• Designed by a musician and music teacher with a Royal Conservatory master's degree




• Download the app and try out the first chapter of each clef for free
• One-time in-app purchase of $4.99 to unlock the full version on all your Android devices


Having a problem? Got a suggestion? You can reach us at hello@completemusicreadingtrainer.com

name: Fishdom
about:

Try challenging and fun match-3 gameplay with unique puzzles as you decorate aquariums to create cozy homes for lovely talking fish. Feed them, play with them, and watch them interact with each other. Hey, your finned friends are waiting for you, so dive in now and enjoy this amazing underwater adventure!

Features:
● Unique gameplay: swap and match pieces, design and decorate aquariums, play with and take care of fish—all in one puzzle game!
● Play hundreds of challenging and fun match-3 levels
● Compete with other players to develop your aquarium even faster
● Explore an exciting aquatic world with funny talking 3D fish that each have their own personality
● Liven up fish tanks with breathtaking underwater decor
● Grab your scuba mask and enjoy amazing aquarium graphics
● It’s a blast for everyone: share your Fishdom mania with your Facebook friends!

Please note that Fishdom is free to play, though some in-game items can also be purchased for real money.
